{
  "stem": "3100.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we found out later that if they wouldn't have liberate us a day before May the 8th, we would have been all killed in that camp because they prepared a place with special that you would have been shot on the top and then the body falls down in a--",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What do you call it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In a deep--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--ditch.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, there was a time when we were free.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We embraced the--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--the Russians with their thanks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think that, at that time, there was-- they called it cholks, the cholks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think that this was given them by the American Army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they said we should leave them alone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They have to go out and liberate more places.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Time is short.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They have to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember I spoke a little Russian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one Russian gave me a piece of chocolate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember it was a Hershey bar.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He got it from the Americans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It came from Americans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know that this probably saved my life because when I left the camp, I weighed maybe 85 pounds, 90 pounds, whatever.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember how it went-- were undernourished.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But this piece of chocolate curbed a little bit my appetite because those who were liberated from the camp after the war, a lot of them died from overeating, you know?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The body is not used to absorb all other, you know--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A huge amount of food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--huge amounts of foods and we were so hungry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was the end.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The end of it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was a mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They gave you a chocolate bar.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Chocolate.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That saved my life.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I found out when we were liberated in Theresienstadt, that there are women too, Jewish women left.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
